♪The wind blows, but I don't see you♪

2
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:14,740
♪I added a few more strokes♪

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,380
♪To the ending♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,140
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:28,220
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

7
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:31,020
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

8
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:33,140
♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 21]

14
00:00:44,790 --> 00:00:45,390
My Lord,

15
00:00:45,390 --> 00:00:46,070
I've ordered

16
00:00:46,070 --> 00:00:47,350
a city-wide search for Her Ladyship.

17
00:00:48,470 --> 00:00:49,320
I know her temperament.

18
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:50,430
If she truly wished to leave,

19
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,070
she wouldn't stay in Canglong City.

20
00:00:52,350 --> 00:00:53,350
Where might Her Ladyship have gone then?

21
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:55,320
Baiyu City.

22
00:01:12,350 --> 00:01:13,120
Lord Ling,

23
00:01:13,870 --> 00:01:15,560
this is Baiyu City.

24
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,430
How dare you act so presumptuously?

25
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,400
Hand her over.

26
00:01:19,710 --> 00:01:21,230
I don't know what you're talking about.

27
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,000
Jing Tian,

28
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,710
if you don't hand over Wan'er,

29
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:32,150
I'll crush your Baiyu City.

30
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,230
Has something happened to Wan'er?

31
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,710
My Lord,

32
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,350
he doesn't seem to be pretending.

33
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,400
Ling Xiao,

34
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,590
explain things clearly.

35
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,350
What happened to Wan'er?

36
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:53,760
Her Ladyship

37
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:55,430
has left the City Lord's Mansion.

38
00:01:56,950 --> 00:01:57,790
Ling Xiao,

39
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,310
what did you do

40
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,790
to make her so heartbroken?

41
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,280
What happened between us

42
00:02:07,510 --> 00:02:08,870
is none of your business.

43
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,310
Ling Xiao,

44
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:13,310
I trusted you to make her happy

45
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,680
when I entrusted her to you.

46
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:18,430
But now it seems

47
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,120
I was gravely mistaken.

48
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,120
Let me tell you,

49
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,150
from now on,

50
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:29,430
I won't give way anymore.

51
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:45,000
Give way?

52
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,280
You don't stand a chance.

53
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:52,150
But she trusts me wholeheartedly.

54
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:54,030
Otherwise, you wouldn't have come

55
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,310
to me first to look for her.

56
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:58,240
You're just afraid
of losing her forever.

57
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,870
I will never ever

58
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:03,310
let go of her.

59
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:06,560
Ling Xiao,

60
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,310
since she has decided to leave,

61
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,630
she won't let you find her easily.

62
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:12,630
Dispatch all the Shadow Guards.

63
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,080
Search every corner.

64
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,470
Find her!

65
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,000
Yes, My Lord.

66
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:16,120
Send our people

67
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,800
to look for Wan'er.

68
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,680
We mustn't let Ling Xiao find her.

69
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:22,360
Yes, My Lord.

70
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,680
Search!

71
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:34,470
Have you seen her?

72
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:36,400
No.

73
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,470
No.

74
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:46,680
We've looked all over.

75
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,360
She isn't here.

76
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:48,630
No one has seen her.

77
00:04:11,940 --> 00:04:17,500
♪The lone snowy peak
is unable to reach the moon♪

78
00:04:17,580 --> 00:04:24,060
♪Gatherings and partings are fated,
love also has its sorrow or joy♪

79
00:04:24,660 --> 00:04:28,580
♪My concern
sinks into the long night♪

80
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:32,620
♪May I be bold to ask what love means?♪

81
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:38,460
♪In the flickering candlelight,
I dream of a glimpse of her♪

82
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:42,340
♪In my dreams,
the past remains unchanged♪

83
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:45,820
♪In my lifetime, sorrows
and joys become a book♪

84
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:52,100
♪I write the rest of my life
with one stroke♪

85
00:04:52,980 --> 00:04:56,300
♪The morning is full of joy♪

86
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,430
Scented pouch!

87
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,220
Come and take a look!

88
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,830
Scented pouch!

89
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:08,920
Please take a look, sir.

90
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:25,020
♪Life's like a lone boat
crossing crimson leaves♪

91
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:28,660
♪Fate is worthy
of sighs and lamentation♪

92
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:32,480
I don't seek

93
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,160
marital bliss.

94
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,630
I only wish for your blessing

95
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,560
to keep my baby safe.

96
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,360
Wait for me there.

97
00:05:49,260 --> 00:05:52,820
♪The morning is full of joy♪

98
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:56,900
♪The evening is full of melancholy♪

99
00:05:57,100 --> 00:06:03,540
♪Miss you a lifetime
with love engraved in my bones♪

100
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:06,360
If there truly are divine beings
in the world,

101
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,600
seeing my deep longing,

102
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,870
why won't they show me a clear path?

103
00:06:17,820 --> 00:06:21,100
♪One glance to see the familiar scenery♪

104
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:25,100
♪One thought to relive
the beginning of us♪

105
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:30,940
♪May we meet again
after countless cycles♪

106
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:40,870
[Half a lifetime of withered affection,
the love is ill-fated]

107
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:45,360
I don't believe in fate.

108
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,000
Her only destiny

109
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,240
is to return to my side.

110
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:56,420
♪Pear blossoms fall
and flowing sleeves feel like yesterday♪

111
00:06:56,540 --> 00:07:02,620
♪The heart is closed,
unable to gaze at the emotional eyes♪

112
00:07:02,740 --> 00:07:05,540
♪This life is filled
with too much affection♪

113
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:09,260
♪Amid the applause,
who can see through it?♪

114
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:14,500
♪Aren't the characters
in the play you and me?♪

115
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:19,260
♪Pear blossoms fall
and birds sing with deep affection♪

116
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:25,860
♪The heart is closed
no matter how romantic it is♪

117
