♪This life is filled
with too much affection♪

118
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:33,180
♪A tale on paper,
whose hearts does it stir?♪

119
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:38,300
♪I'm afraid the characters
in the play aren't us♪

120
00:07:38,300 --> 00:07:39,270
[Whether you love me or hate me,
I will never let go.]

121
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:40,430
Whether you love me or hate me,

122
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,830
I will never let go.

123
