♪People sit silently
by candlelight as night begins♪

124
00:07:56,820 --> 00:08:02,540
♪A play of sorrows and joys,
your role, my outline♪

125
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:07,820
♪Though the dream is over,
the feelings are hard to let go♪

126
00:08:07,940 --> 00:08:09,500
♪Everyone is filled
with sorrow and pity♪

127
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:13,380
♪Alas, the mortal world
has too many spectators♪

128
